text: Buranchino () is a rural locality (a village) in Duvan-Mechetlinsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 191 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye, 3 km from Duvan-Mechetlino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Buranchino
